Subject: Printing Blocked
Description: We have a user trying to print an email and is getting immediately blocked with no option to remediate. When looking at the CAP logs there is a log for a policy that does not exist called Browser Printing and for Predefined Content that we do not use as an Item Type. He is not trying to print from a browser.
What_We_Know__c: The Customer confirmed that they are using the latest server version but with an older epp client. We have suggested to upgrade the client to the latest version, reboot the computer and retest the print scenario.
Next_Steps__c: We are waiting for the customer to confirm if the issue is reproducible with the latest epp client version.
Solution_Comment__c:
The Customer confirmed that they are using the latest server version but with an older epp client. 
We have suggested to upgrade the client to the latest version, reboot the computer and retest the print scenario.
The issue is no longer reproducible after the latest epp client has been installed.
